OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChilly start, then bright
OL,6,Fspells through the morning but cloud
OL,7,Fthickens through the afternoon,
OL,8,Fperhaps bringing some patchy light
OL,9,Frain eastwards later. Winds generally
OL,10,Flight and variable.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy to start becoming
OL,13,Fovercast with rain moving in from the
OL,14,Fwest after midnight and moving slowly
OL,15,Feastwards. The wind will increase and
OL,16,Fbecome breezy by the morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FRain and strong winds early
OL,19,FSaturday, followed by sunshine and
OL,20,Fblustery showers. Temperatures mostly
OL,21,Faround average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
